  "time_ut": 1656939298,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dbd\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0dad\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0ddd \u0daf\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db6\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two youths trapped in the water are rescued",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A police lifeguard team has gone there and rescued two youths who were trapped in a wasteland in the Haragama area of \u200b\u200bVictoria Reservoir by opening several sluice gates due to the rise in the water level of Polgolla Reservoir due to the torrential rain that hit the Kandy area for the past few days.",
        "The sluice gates of the Polgolla reservoir were opened and at around 03.00 in the evening, the two young men were trapped in the middle of the respective island.",
        "In this regard, after being informed by the Talatuoya Police, under the guidance of Chief Inspector Yapa, Station Commander of the Kandy Division Police Lifeguard Unit attached to Dalada Maligawa Police, female Police Sergeant 1721 Jayanthi, Police Sergeant 61265 Mangala, Police Constable Hathai 73092 Premalal, and Suvechcha Lifeguard Officer Krinsnarathne went there within minutes. After a 45-hour operation, they were safely brought to land using ropes.",
        "A resident of Gurudeniya area and two residents of Nuwara Eliya area were rescued."
      ],
